plt.title("Perth Weather Forecast")
plt.show()


ğŸ‘‰ Here your X-axis = dates, Y-axis = temperature values

âš™ï¸ 3. Customize X and Y Axis Limits

You can control the axis range using plt.xlim() and plt.ylim():

